---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section id="services" class="section-container">
  <h2 class="section-title">Services I Offer</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
    <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
        <Icon name="mdi:web" class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 text-center">Web Development</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center leading-relaxed">
        Building scalable, high-performance web and mobile applications with React, Next.js, and Astro. Experienced in developing user-focused solutions with clean architecture, modern design systems, and optimized infrastructure for reliability and speed.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">React</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Next.js</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Astro</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
        <Icon name="mdi:file-document-alert-outline" class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 text-center">QA & Technical Documentation</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center leading-relaxed">
        Authored and maintain 150+ technical articles reaching 60,000+ readers annually. Led integration of AI-powered support systems achieving 64.6% automated resolution rate and 90.2% customer satisfaction. Experienced in QA workflows, knowledge base management, and support automation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Markdown</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Custom AI flows</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Figma</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Intercom</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
        <Icon name="mdi:face-agent" class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 text-center">Cloud Infrastructure & Operations</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center leading-relaxed">
        Managing cloud infrastructure on Google Cloud Platform and Cloudflare with 99% uptime. Experienced in system administration, platform migrations, incident response, and operational reliability. Skilled in Windows/Linux environments, scripting, and infrastructure automation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">GCP</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Cloudflare</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Azure</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Intercom</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs rounded">Linear</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 